WEBVTT

1
00:00:18.852 --> 00:00:22.268
- I remember it was Sunday
morning after Thanksgiving.


2
00:00:22.351 --> 00:00:24.185
I was 11 years old,

3
00:00:24.268 --> 00:00:25.143
and I had spent the night

4
00:00:25.226 --> 00:00:28.019
at my best friend Tracy's
house.


5
00:00:29.602 --> 00:00:31.810
The clock radio went off
and woke me up,


6
00:00:31.894 --> 00:00:33.477
and I heard a news report say

7
00:00:33.560 --> 00:00:37.226
my mom's body was found
off the coast of Catalina.


8
00:00:39.852 --> 00:00:41.852
The next thing I knew,
my stepdad's driver


9
00:00:41.935 --> 00:00:45.185
was there with our nanny,
Willie Mae.


10
00:00:45.268 --> 00:00:47.852
They had come to pick me up
and take me home.


11
00:00:49.810 --> 00:00:52.019
It had rained,
and the streets were wet,


12
00:00:52.101 --> 00:00:55.351
and I was asking,
"Is Mommy okay?"


13
00:00:55.435 --> 00:00:57.393
