17
00:01:06.810 --> 00:01:09.393
I said, "Maybe she just has
a broken leg


18
00:01:09.477 --> 00:01:13.060
or something like that."

19
00:01:13.143 --> 00:01:16.143
Then my stepdad came back.

20
00:01:16.226 --> 00:01:19.769
I went down the steps,
and I could tell,


21
00:01:19.852 --> 00:01:22.727
just when I looked
at his face,


22
00:01:22.810 --> 00:01:24.602
that something awful
had happened.


23
00:01:27.101 --> 00:01:30.560
The day my mom died,
my entire world was shattered,


24
00:01:30.643 --> 00:01:33.226
